        <p data-uuid="079c74e51b0247dc88825bbc1a089b95">By late 1968 more than a million tons of explosives had been dropped on North and South Vietnam. Many Vietnamese soldiers and civilians were killed. The Communists’ ability to wage war, however, was not destroyed.</p>
